| 5 | GĐ1 workflow | `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/04_Process_Flow.md` → `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/04_*_Flow.md` → `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/06_Workflow_Status.md` → `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/07_Sequence_Diagram.md` |
